-- Arab Bank Confirms Resignation of Chairman Abdul Hamid Shoman
-- B y   M o h a m m a d   T a y s e e r
-- 2012-08-16T15:43:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-16/arab-bank-confirms-resignation-of-chairman-abdul-hamid-shoman.html
Arab Bank (ARBK)  Plc Chairman Abdul Hamid Shoman resigned today, the bank said in an e-mailed statement.  “It is unfortunate that we confirm the resignation of
Shoman from the bank’s board of directors,” Sabih Masri, the
bank’s deputy chairman, said in the statement. It was Shoman’s
personal decision to resign, Masri said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mohammad Tayseer in Amman, Jordan, through the Dubai newsroom at
   mtayseer@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Louis Meixler at 
